article: How to Manifest Anything You Desire: A Beginner’s Guide
intro: Manifestation is the basic idea that you can achieve your goals and desires through positive thinking and willpower.

steps.subtitle: There’s no rules on what you can and can’t manifest. At the end of the day, if it’s something you deeply want, it can be manifested. If you’re not sure what you want to try and manifest, use these ideas to spark some inspiration:
sub-points: A lovely relationship with a family member
